              "free_text": [
                " B-10 F3 COUNTER, 2.5 CM DIAMETER, APPROXIMATEL",
                " TWELVE CM LONG AND FILLED WITH ARGON AT 1 ATMOSPHERE",
                " AND 10 CM OF BF3 ENRICHED TO 90 PERCENT IN B-10.",
                " TO MINIMISE END AND WALL EFFECTS THE COUNTER WAS",
                " MOUNTED WITH ITS AXIS PERPENDICULAR TO THE NEUTRON",
                " BEAM, WHICH HAD A DIAMETER LESS THAN THE ACTIVE",
                " LENGTH OF THE COUNTER."
              ]
            }
          ],
